#. type: <p></p>
#: securing-debian-howto.en.sgml:61 en/appendix.sgml:321
msgid ""
"Generally, disable gratuitous services in <file>/etc/inetd.conf</file> using "
"<prgn>update-inetd --disable</prgn> (or disable <prgn>inetd</prgn> "
