"of introducing the ruleset line by line through the command line) and, as a "
"precaution, keep a backdoor<footnote><p>Such as <em>knockd</em>. "
"Alternatively, you can open a different console and have the system ask for "
"confirmation that there is somebody on the other side, and reset the "
"firewall chain if no confirmation is given. The following test script could "
"be of use: <example>#!/bin/bash while true; do read -n 1 -p \"Are you there? "
